    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the slightly undulating wooden surface finished with an adze, a type of axe with the blade set at right angles to the handle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
